is not happy with your attitude.

00:02:47.458 --> 00:02:48.999
If you still stick to your decision...

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.542
of not supporting the British
during the War...

00:02:54.250 --> 00:02:56.082
We'll have to take
some very hard decisions.

00:02:56.083 --> 00:02:59.417
Whereby I'll be forced to resign, huh?

00:02:59.924 --> 00:03:02.215
Listen Jawahar, come what may...

00:03:02.958 --> 00:03:07.707
I'll never support the Empire
which mercilessly ruled over
us for 200 years.

00:03:07.708 --> 00:03:12.333
And I will never support the sacrifice
of Indian soldiers for the British cause.

00:03:12.375 --> 00:03:15.917
If they have to fight,
they should fight for India, their motherland.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:19.333
Violence through military struggle,
even in self-defence...

00:03:19.792 --> 00:03:21.458
is not a solution, Subhas.

00:03:22.250 --> 00:03:26.792
Non-violence,as shown by Bapu,
has to be the way forward.

00:03:27.875 --> 00:03:29.292
Very well.

00:03:29.317 --> 00:03:31.358
Let us assume we do go forward.

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.832
India does win freedom.

00:03:32.833 --> 00:03:36.375
And
you are
the first Prime Minister,
Jawahar.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:41.150
Do you envisage an army, a navy,
and an air force for Free India?

00:03:41.333 --> 00:03:45.208
Or do you think the best way
to encounter foreign aggression...

00:03:45.292 --> 00:03:47.291
