00:03:47.292 --> 00:03:49.167
- Whatever it is...
- Jawahar.

00:03:50.145 --> 00:03:53.562
Subhas, just think about it.

00:03:55.827 --> 00:03:58.910
The British Empire is in a lot of trouble
right now.

00:03:59.378 --> 00:04:02.128
If we help them now...

00:04:02.698 --> 00:04:06.739
then I believe,
they'll give in to our demands.

00:04:07.208 --> 00:04:11.083
But Bapu, we had helped them
during the First World War too.

00:04:11.390 --> 00:04:13.348
What did we get in return?

00:04:13.617 --> 00:04:16.325
Rowlatt Act. Jallianwala Bagh.

00:04:16.976 --> 00:04:18.601
It won't be repeated this time.

00:04:19.207 --> 00:04:20.874
I am very certain.

00:04:21.276 --> 00:04:24.109
In time, we'll win our freedom.

00:04:24.183 --> 00:04:25.340
How long, Bapu?

00:04:26.277 --> 00:04:27.129
And why?

00:04:28.333 --> 00:04:31.292
We shouldn't be begging for freedom.
It's our right!

00:04:31.333 --> 00:04:34.167
We can't ask for freedom.
We have seize it from them.

00:04:34.558 --> 00:04:37.183
Your way of thinking
is completely wrong, Subhas.

00:04:37.362 --> 00:04:39.528
Violence is not the way.

00:04:39.958 --> 00:04:44.708
The only way India can attain independence
is through non-violence.

00:04:44.750 --> 00:04:46.792
That's what I believe.

00:05:09.784 --> 00:05:11.042
Please forgive me, Bapu.

00:05:12.036 --> 00:05:13.550
I don't agree with you.

00:05:15.583 --> 00:05:17.888
You can fight for freedom
in your own way.

00:05:18.583 --> 00:05:19.974
