And we
would like to dedicate
our success...

00:37:24.000 --> 00:37:26.250
in this struggle for independence...

00:37:26.375 --> 00:37:29.082
to the brave sons
of our beloved
motherland...

00:37:29.083 --> 00:37:32.250
who gave up their lives fighting
for this country.

